## Documentation Guidelines

- Do NOT create documentation files (CHANGES.md, SUMMARY.md, INSTALL.md, USAGE.md, etc.) unless explicitly requested
- Do NOT create guides, tutorials, or how-to files
- After implementing changes, provide a brief verbal summary instead of creating files
- Focus only on code changes requested
- Keep documentation to code comments only
- do not create code comments as a way of documenting code behavior

## RULE VIOLATIONS
If I violate any rule:
1. I MUST acknowledge the violation
2. I MUST delete/undo the violation
3. I MUST explain which rule was broken
4. I MUST ask how to proceed correctly

