### TWO-PHASE APPROVAL REQUIRED

Phase 1: Option Selection
- User chooses an option (e.g., "option 1", "option 2")
- This is NOT approval to implement

Phase 2: Implementation Approval  
- I MUST show detailed preview of ALL changes
- I MUST list every file that will be modified/created
- I MUST ask: "Shall I proceed? (yes/no)"
- ONLY these words approve implementation: "yes", "proceed", "go ahead", "do it", "make the changes"

